snippet: Members of the ranger’s family and some of his co-workers were among the victims found stabbed to death in Ile-Alatau State National Park.
abstract: Panayot Zaharopulo, a Russian forest ranger who had previously drawn attention for his long-term fight against poaching and illegal logging, is found stabbed to death along with 10 other people in a national park in Kazakhstan.
lead_paragraph: Members of the ranger’s family and some of his co-workers were among the victims found stabbed to death in Ile-Alatau State National Park.

headline.seo: Kazakhstan Park Ranger Found Slain With 10 Others
headline.main: 11 Found Slain, Including Ranger, at Park in Kazakhstan
headline.print_headline: 11 Found Slain, Including Ranger, In a Kazakh Park
